Package: argus-insight-agent
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.11), systemd
Description: Argus Insight Agent - Server management agent
 Argus Insight Agent is a server management agent that provides
 command execution, server resource monitoring, application
 installation/management, and remote terminal capabilities.
 .
 It runs as a systemd service with root privileges and exposes
 a REST/WebSocket API for remote management.
